deck: Toby Kebbell is an English actor, primarily known for his villainous roles in 'Dawn of the Planet of the Apes' and 'Fantastic Four'.
description:
Comic Related Roles

Koba

Kebbell, utilizing performance capture technology, played Koba, the primary antagonist of the Matt Reeves-directed film Dawn of the Planet of the Apes. The film is a sequel to the 2011 reboot of the Planet of the Apes franchise, Rise of the Planet of the Apes. Koba is the second in command to Caesar, and attempts to usurp his role as ape leader after disagreeing with his methods.

Victor Domashev - Doom

Kebbell plays Victor Domashev, otherwise known as Doom in the 2015 film Fantastic Four. The film, directed by Josh Trank, is billed as a contemporary re-imagining of the Fantastic Four franchise.
name: Toby Kebbell
